headline.print_headline: Depor Fan Killed in Clashes Before Atletico Game
headline.main: Depor Fan Killed in Clashes Before Atletico Game

lead_paragraph: A Deportivo La Coruna supporter died after dozens of rival fans from radical groups clashed before the club's La Liga match at Atletico Madrid on Sunday.
